rows.label: bf04120165_0040
rows.name: So you are my new Driver.

rows.label: bf04120165_0050
rows.name:
Bit of a scrawny one, if you ask me,
but ah well. It's good to meet you.

rows.label: bf04120165_0070
rows.name: He talks kind of like Vandham, huh.

rows.label: bf04120165_0090
rows.name:
Oh, right... You wouldn't remember,
since you've been reawakened now.

rows.label: bf04120165_0120
rows.name: Ah, so my core was passed down to you.

rows.label: bf04120165_0140
rows.name: I didn't sense any guilt in your words.

rows.label: bf04120165_0150
rows.name: Hmm...you're a perceptive one, all right.

rows.label: bf04120165_0160
rows.name:
Yes, you take after your old master
in more ways than one.

rows.label: bf04120165_0170
rows.name:
Listen, Suzaku. We need your help.
Reckon you could clear the way for us?

rows.label: bf04120165_0180
rows.name:
This stuff? Of course.
Nothing simpler.
